snippet.title: Exoprimal x Street Fighter 6 Collaboration Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
From the Fighting Grounds to the war games, Exoprimal x Street Fighter 6 customizations have been authorized for deployment in fall 2023.
Reminder: Exofighters never back down.
#Exoprimal #StreetFighter6 #Capcom
